title: Cambridge Texts in the History of Philosophy - 30 volumes
description:
A series of new translations of various philosophical classics -- Plato, Aristotle, Augustine, Thomas Aquinas, Descartes, Kant, Hume, etc.

Most volumes are in high quality PDF format; a few are in CHM format.
